div.span:
Target cannot use its held item for five turns. If the target leaves the field, this effect ends.
If a Pokmon under this effect uses bug bite or pluck on a Pokmon holding a berry, the berry is destroyed but not used. If a Pokmon under this effect uses fling, it will fail.
This effect is passed by baton pass.

div.div: Cocrystalus is an ominous legend that lurks in dark catacombs. Its enigmatic powers enchant all nearby, sealing power in life-crushing embargo.
